channel.title: What file is for changing NPC name(renamed)
channel.description: I know its class5 in non renamed but what is it in renamed? Someone please tell me

item.title: What file is for changing NPC name(renamed)
item.dc:creator: @FusionLord FusionLord
item.description:
@FusionLord wrote:

Nom Nom:

Use common sense. Find something that is in class5, then see if it’s in one of the renamed files.

Did you not read what he wrote his client files are renamed, He
does not have and class#.java files he has a refactored client!

[on topic]
Download a non-refactored client and search in the class5.java
for a piece of code that DOESN’T have
the text “class5” in it then search for that piece of code in the
refactored files.
